;;; Regexp at end catches Benezit abreviated museum forms.
;;; \\|\\(\\(Mus\\..\\)\\(\\(\\(Nat\\..\\)\\|\\(Mod..\\)\\|\\(d'Art.\\)\\)+\\)+?\\)
